<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-5">
        <h1>Business Information</h1>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
            <a asp-action="Manage" class="btn btn-primary">Edit Business Info</a>
            <a asp-action="About" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">View Public Page</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===================== HERO SECTION (LOGO + TAGLINE) ===================== -->
    <div class="hero-section">
        <img src="~/images/logo.jpg" alt="Dynamic Ice Inc Logo" />
        <h2>Dynamic Ice Inc</h2>
        <p>Keeping Cool, Keeping Control — Revolutionizing Beverage Refrigeration</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ===================== DYNAMIC ICE INC BUSINESS OVERVIEW ===================== -->
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-header">
            <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Welcome to Dynamic Ice Inc</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p style="line-height:1.8; color:#2c3e50;">
                <strong>Dynamic Ice Inc</strong> is a forward-thinking company specializing in providing
                refrigeration solutions for beverage manufacturers and distributors. Founded on
                <strong>10 February 2025</strong>, our mission is to revolutionize the traditional methods of
                managing beverage refrigeration assets through innovation and technology.
            </p>

            <p style="line-height:1.8; color:#2c3e50;">
                We provide and manage fridges for retailers, spaza shops, and shebeens across South Africa,
                ensuring that beverages remain perfectly chilled while empowering our customers with data-driven insights
                into fridge performance, maintenance, and inventory.
            </p>

            <p style="line-height:1.8; color:#2c3e50;">
                As part of the <strong>ONT3010 3rd Year Project</strong>, we developed the
                <strong>Fridge Management System (FMS)</strong> — a powerful web-based platform that enhances
                operational efficiency, automates communication, and integrates key business operations
                such as customer management, fridge tracking, fault reporting, maintenance scheduling,
                and supplier purchasing.
            </p>

            <h6 class="mt-4" style="font-weight:600;">🧩 Our System Subsystems</h6>
            <ul class="overview-list" style="line-height:1.8; color:#2c3e50;">
                <li><strong>Administration Subsystem:</strong> Core of operations managing customers, employees, and fridge locations.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Management Subsystem:</strong> Manages customer data, fridge allocations, and inventory tracking.</li>
                <li><strong>Fridge Fault Subsystem:</strong> Handles fault reports, technician scheduling, and repair tracking.</li>
                <li><strong>Fridge Maintenance Subsystem:</strong> Manages service records and maintenance scheduling for optimal performance.</li>
                <li><strong>Purchasing Subsystem:</strong> Streamlines supplier management and procurement processes.</li>
            </ul>

            <h6 class="mt-4" style="font-weight:600;">🎯 Our Vision</h6>
            <p style="line-height:1.8; color:#2c3e50;">
                Dynamic Ice Inc aims to become a leader in digital refrigeration management by integrating
                smart systems that minimize downtime, optimize maintenance efficiency, and improve
                transparency between suppliers, technicians, and customers.
            </p>

            <blockquote class="blockquote mt-3" style="font-style:italic; color:#764ba2;">
                “Keeping Cool, Keeping Control — Dynamic Ice Inc.”
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- ===================== END BUSINESS OVERVIEW ===================== -->
    <!-- ===================== EXISTING CONTENT ===================== -->
